reviewText: He loves it.  Watches every day
Great cartoons and I'd definitely recommend this to anyone with children. While being an entertaining cartoon, it also teaches them good values.

My son loves this show and it is no longer on where I live.  I had them on my DVR but it broke so I was happy to find the DVDs.  It is cute show, nice animation, as cheesy as most kid shows, but oh well.
We have volume I and II. Although it caters to the cliches of young boys, it has valuable lessons for them to learn from. Good entertainment for my toddler.

Turbo Dogs is a great DVD for children who love dogs. The Turbo Dogs are car racers and each episode has a good moral story along with plenty of action. If you love Sesame St and their DVD's, this is another terrific one to own.
